# No inline styles

Do not use:

- `style={{ ... }}`
- `style={someObject}`

Instead use one of:

- Colocated CSS file per component folder (preferred): `styles.css` or `styles.module.css`
- Shared stylesheet(s) in `src/styles/` for truly global layout/typography
- Ant Design theming tokens via `ConfigProvider` / `theme.ts` for design-system consistency

## Examples

Bad:

```tsx
<div style={{ width: '86%' }} />
```

Good (CSS):

```tsx
<div className={styles.meterFill} />
```

```css
.meterFill { width: 86%; }
```

